28#ifndef QRCODEPAINTER_H
29#define QRCODEPAINTER_H
30
31#include <QImage>
32#include <QBrush>
33#include <QPainter>
34
35#include "qtqrcode.h"
36
37class QtQrCodePainter
38{
39public:
40 QtQrCodePainter(float margin = 0.0, const QBrush &background = Qt::white,
41 const QBrush &foreground = Qt::black);
42 ~QtQrCodePainter();
43
44 void paint(const QtQrCode &qrCode, QPainter &painter);
45 void paint(const QtQrCode &qrCode, QPainter &painter, int width, int height);
46 void paint(const QtQrCode &qrCode, QPainter &painter, int painterWidth);
47 QImage toImage(const QtQrCode &qrCode, int size);
48 bool saveSvg(const QtQrCode &qrCode, const QString &fileName, int size);
49
50 inline float margin() const { return m_margin; }
51 inline bool setMargin(float margin)
52 {
53 if (m_margin != margin) {
54 m_margin = margin;
55 return true;
56 }
57 return false;
58 }
59
60 inline const QBrush &background() const { return m_background; }
61 inline bool setBackground(const QBrush &background)
62 {
63 if (m_background != background) {
64 m_background = background;
65 return true;
66 }
67 return false;
68 }
69
70 inline const QBrush &foreground() const { return m_foreground; }
71 inline bool setForeground(const QBrush &foreground)
72 {
73 if (m_foreground != foreground) {
74 m_foreground = foreground;
75 return true;
76 }
77 return false;
78 }
79
80private:
81 float m_margin;
82 float m_offsetX;
83 float m_offsetY;
84 bool m_svgPaint;
85 QBrush m_background;
86 QBrush m_foreground;
87};
88
89#endif // QRCODEPAINTER_H
